    public class CheckBoxTreeViewDialog
extends org.eclipse.jface.dialogs.Dialog
    The purpose of this dialog is to display the content of a 'normal' TreeViewer in a CheckboxTreeViewer to select some of it's content and then export it to *.csv.
    Author:
    Dominik Hamann, Patrick Haese
    See Also:
    CsvExporter
